{"tid":827102,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"之前好有自信覺得男朋友唔會偷食，而家變到好不安","createTime":"2018-09-18T16:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T01:30:53.000Z","uid":195089,"like":17,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d804cd1e30fa4a673e19383809b2251e9053ec09","tid":827102,"uid":195089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"前排發現到男朋友whatsapp有個曖昧對象<br />\n我地兩個真正係埋一齊之前佢地已經識<br />\n我見到我地一齊咗之後，有次我地去街嗰陣佢見到一樣令佢諗起個女仔嘅嘢佢仲影相send俾佢<br />\n我覺得個女仔唔知佢已經有我，因為佢冇係facebook ig嗰啲公開過我，平時亦唔會tag我<br />\n<br />\n而家見到男朋友ig post啲食飯相或者會impress到女仔嘅相，就覺得佢係咪扮緊一個好有品味識飲識食會周圍去嘅單身男士<br />\n就算出街影相有影埋我，都會post張冇我嘅相，或者淨係post一份嘢食，好似想營造得自己一個嘅感覺<br />\n我覺得好討厭，但係以前聽人講，唔想分手或者離婚就一定要扮唔知<br />\n我仲要唔知除咗whatsapp仲有冇其他地方有曖昧對象<br />\n<br />\n係咪覺得精神出軌就唔係偷食？<br />\n係咪覺得齋用電話flirt就唔係出軌？<br />\n係咪拍緊拖都keep住有曖昧對象好common？<br />\n係咪要靠好多個女仔鍾意自己嚟滿足自尊心？"},{"pid":"aad6a1347d91c93af494882e8abc30af54bc73c4","tid":827102,"uid":56586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"橙"},{"pid":"f5813a043187ef19aa09ffbe2316c6334abfe38a","tid":827102,"uid":8500,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"100%會偷食"},{"pid":"81dd53cc5ccf2385e9f8c90c53889a2bd7a3ed0c","tid":827102,"uid":163291,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"係咪覺得精神出軌就唔係偷食？<br />\n<strong>係<br />\n有精神出軌個刻開始<br />\n根本係等緊機會變埋肉體出軌</strong><br />\n係咪覺得齋用電話flirt就唔係出軌？<br />\n<strong>係出緊軌，flirt完等埋齋</strong><br />\n係咪拍緊拖都keep住有曖昧對象好common？<br />\n<strong>唔係</strong><br />\n係咪要靠好多個女仔鍾意自己嚟滿足自尊心？<br />\n<strong>唔係，係人問題</strong>"},{"pid":"9634a0bd7f836ce575f41fd7e0c3774dbbbfdf3b","tid":827102,"uid":158114,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"男人好鐘意偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f175370459f163fc66c44b28e44754f2f4796159","tid":827102,"uid":16594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"我都同你一樣 好有信心男朋友唔偷食<br />\n但有時感情既係脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c474ac342df0f9a57d2b5ac7d7b80f7b27f562","tid":827102,"uid":205566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:34:09.000Z","msg":"點解冇公開都咁有自信男朋友唔會偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04a012679a38fbedde899d749ef870897f33f5a","tid":827102,"uid":200414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:39:20.000Z","msg":"啲男人就係咁<br />\n同你一齊之後就會掛住溝唔到嗰個<br />\n屌佢老母"},{"pid":"bdf2c5a2ccb49504e115b7ae9bcb77d300c2737d","tid":827102,"uid":140492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:42:03.000Z","msg":"由佢無公開你就知個男人想偷食啦<br />\n唔好咁笨啦 早d分手對你好d"},{"pid":"2ebd7501a7ecd398df8dd41b518aa59d49791bb5","tid":827102,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T23:56:36.000Z","msg":"好人好者做咩唔公開"},{"pid":"df3414d5d8af6f8d1b3ab93430317dc89bc22ca7","tid":827102,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T23:58:39.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"4b4ba316012edc83da8bea6d998ba05bb9d17a6b","tid":827102,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T00:01:13.000Z","msg":"你男朋友未溝到果條女咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23dedae90401a4b0eae12e14969f07138b3564d2","tid":827102,"uid":195089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c474ac342df0f9a57d2b5ac7d7b80f7b27f562","tid":827102,"uid":205566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:34:09.000Z","msg":"點解冇公開都咁有自信男朋友唔會偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:01:37.000Z","msg":"因為會去佢屋企過夜，佢屋企人都係度<br />\n同埋平時佢見朋友我都會在場，多數全男班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔記得咗有上網撩女仔呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{